  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You can lick yourself or your allies using chakra-enhanced saliva to heal wounds. <br />You may lick a number of creatures up to your proficiency bonus, and they cannot benefit from this feature again until they complete a long rest. The saliva's effects last for 8 hours.<br />Any creature you lick gains 2d8 temporary hit points and reduces the rank of burned, corroded, poisoned, bleeding, or lacerated conditions by 2, if applicable.<br />You may lick one creature as an action or multiple creatures during the duration of a short rest.</p>",
